nodes.text: This Mon Calamari was one of the many Mon Calamari prisoners taken captive by the Separatists on Dac during the Battle of Mon Cala and transported to an underwater cave used as a prison camp. Prince Lee-Char, along with padawan Ahsoka Tano, managed to get inside the camp and talk to him and the other prisoners, motivating them and telling them not to lose hope.
